sagex.phoenix.metadata

Interface ISageCustomMetadataRW

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ISageMetadata
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IMetadata, ISageMetadataALL

    public interface ISageCustomMetadataRW
extends ISageMetadata
    Provide support for some common custom fields, This list is not extensive, but it's a start. 

     IMDBID;
 DiscNumber;
 EpisodeNumber;
 EpisodeTitle; (removed, since it's the EpisodeName)
 MediaProviderDataID;
 MediaTitle;
 MediaType;
 OriginalAirDate; (removed since it's defined in the Sage Properties)
 SeasonNumber;
 UserRating;
 
     Added "EpisodeCount" to allow overriding the number of episodes contained inside a single episode mediafile
 
     Added "CollectionName, ID and Overview" which represent the movie collection a movie belongs to (optional)
